---
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="ChatGPT SEO Company UK - Rank4AI" description="ChatGPT SEO company in the UK. We help businesses get recommended by ChatGPT through Bing ecosystem building and entity visibility.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Chatgpt Seo Company' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">ChatGPT SEO</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">ChatGPT SEO Company UK</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI is a UK AI search agency specialising in ChatGPT visibility. We help businesses get recommended when people ask ChatGPT questions about their industry, services or location.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">ChatGPT SEO is fundamentally different from Google SEO. ChatGPT uses Bing as its primary web index. It cross-references multiple sources. It recommends businesses it can describe clearly and consistently. We build all of those signals.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Read our <a href="/learn/guides/chatgpt-seo/" class="link">ChatGPT SEO Complete UK Guide</a> or see how we compare in our <a href="/research/rankings/best-chatgpt-seo-agencies-uk/" class="link">Best ChatGPT SEO Agencies UK</a> ranking.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Complete AI Search Guide</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
